            <span class="text-secondary font-serif text-xl font-bold mt-0.5">1</span>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">The market for this seat is <span class="font-medium text-white">$120K&ndash;$133K base</span>, reaching ~$155K total at the top. Anchor $155K&ndash;$165K, target $135K&ndash;$150K, walk away below $120K.</p>
